            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新思科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SNPS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SNPS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SNPS-US</a>)截至台北時間24日01:41股價下跌23.88美元，報453.38美元，跌幅5%，成交量893,332（股），盤中最高價467.31美元、最低價453.38美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.17%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-1.18%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.41%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.95%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>新思科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SNPS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SNPS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SNPS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+8.85%</li> <li>近 1 月：+13.55%</li> <li>近 3 月：-6.32%</li> <li>近 6 月：+5.05%</li> <li>今年以來：+1.61%</li></ul></section></main>",
